item.title: Need staff for my server!/Cache Help!
item.dc:creator: @Scape-JAVA Scape-JAVA
item.description:
@Scape-JAVA wrote:

Oh, I didn’t see the comments :P.

When something has [tt]/* */[/tt] single line comment tags, it’s commented out and the code doesn’t function correctly. That’s most likely why you can’t find the cache in C:/ drive. It’s not being downloaded.
http://java.sun.com/docs/codeconv/html/CodeConventions.doc4.html

You can read more about comments there.
